item.title: CVE-2017-5799|2024-09-16T20:03:01.696Z -- hewlett%20packard%20enterprise -- opencall%20media%20platform%20%28ocmp%29
item.description: A Remote Code Execution vulnerability in HPE OpenCall Media Platform (OCMP) was found. The vulnerability impacts OCMP versions prior to 3.4.2 RP201 (for OCMP 3.x), all versions prior to 4.4.7 RP702 (for OCMP 4.x).
